 World Cup China 1991|format=PDF}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{FIFA player|344}}\n* {{soccerway}}\n\n{{Brazil squad 1991 FIFA Women's World Cup}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=January 2017}}\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Rocha, Rosangela}}\n[[Category:1962 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Brazilian women's footballers]]\n[[Category:Brazil women's international footballers]]\n[[Category:Brazilian footballers]]\n[[Category:Place of birth missing (living people)]]\n[[Category:1991 FIFA Women's World Cup players]]\n[[Category:Women's association football midfielders]]\n{{Brazil-women-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Brazilian footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n|name           = Danda\n|image          =\n|image_size     =\n|caption        =\n|fullname       = Ros\u00e2ngela Rocha<ref>https://footfy.com/futebol-feminino/meninas-entram-em-cena-em-busca-do-titulo-inedito/</ref>\n|birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1962|11|19|df=y}}\n|birth_place    =\n|death_date     =\n|death_place    =\n|height         =\n|position       = [[Midfielder]]\n|youthyears1    =\n|youthclubs1    =\n|years1         =\n|clubs1         = [[EC Radar]]\n|caps1          =\n|goals1         =\n|years2         =\n|clubs2         =\n|caps2          =\n|goals2         =\n|totalcaps      =\n|totalgoals     =\n|nationalyears1 =\n|nationalteam1  = [[Brazil women's national football team|Brazil]]\n|nationalcaps1  =\n|nationalgoals1 =\n| manageryears1  =\n| managerclubs1  =\n| medaltemplates =\n|club-update    =\n|nationalteam-update =16 November 1991 (before the [[1991 FIFA Women's World Cup]])\n}}\n'''Ros\u00e2ngela Rocha''' (born 19 November 1962), commonly known as '''Danda''',<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.facebook.com/avitrineff/posts/2172960326105926 |title=Copa do Mundo de Futebol Feminino 1991 \u2013 China |trans-title=Women's World Cup 1991 \u2013 China |publisher=A Vitrine do Futebol Feminino |date=8 June 2019 |